{
  "stem": "15396.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And, of course, there's these wonderful people.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "The people who-- I was an errand boy.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I wasn't a member of the-- of the brain trust.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "There was Daniel Benedict, of course, who died and-- and Hirschman.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "We called him Beamish, very, very brilliant and enormous help to Fry.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "In fact, he was-- I think a lot of the, for example, the way over the mountains, he had been in the French-- in the Spanish Civil War.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "He knew how to get over the mountains.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "A lot of things that he did were brilliant.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And he had a lot of courage.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And he was Jewish, of course.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And then Jean Gemahling, who also was absolutely brilliant in underground things and all.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And-- and then Benedict, Daniel Benedict, he's the one who told me about the-- the gangsters, how to get in with the gangsters and all.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Marseille.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They started an organization, a cover to-- American Secours-- to help people by giving them money and so forth.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And-- although they had a lot of trouble getting money.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Of course, we were volunteers.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But in fact, I think everybody in it were volunteers.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Maybe one or two secretaries had to be-- have their hotel paid.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But it was an organization to cover what we were doing, trying to smuggle these people out.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, and then-- then I was in Marseille.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I did one or two little things, like I met some friends who thought of a brilliant idea of getting a boat to take people out, and trying to get a British warship to pick them up, which was a pretty stupid idea because it was-- you know, we were kids.",
      "word_count": 52
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We didn't-- everything we did was dumb.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I had a friend-- friend, someone I knew, named Freddie McEvoy.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
